---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Veneers — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Custom porcelain veneers in Huntington Beach. Transform your smile with thin, natural-looking shells tailored to you. Dr. Jason Fu at Oasis Dental Care. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">Veneers</span></div>
    <span class="tag">Cosmetic dentistry</span>
    <h1>Veneers</h1>
    <p>Thin, custom porcelain layers for a brighter, more balanced smile.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Close-up of natural-looking veneers in warm lighting</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>A custom solution, tailored to your smile.</h2>
          <p>Veneers are thin porcelain shells bonded to the front of teeth to improve color, shape, and proportion. Each veneer is custom-tailored to fit your unique smile.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>What Veneers Can Address</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Staining that doesn't respond to whitening</li>
            <li>Chipped or slightly broken teeth</li>
            <li>Gaps between front teeth</li>
            <li>Uneven or irregularly shaped teeth</li>
            <li>Worn-down enamel</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Before/after veneer smile — natural, not overdone</span>
          </div>

          <h3>The Process</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Consultation and shade selection</li>
            <li>Minimal enamel preparation</li>
            <li>Custom veneer fabrication</li>
            <li>Bonding and bite adjustment</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Dr. Fu reviewing veneer shade with patient</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Porcelain vs. Composite Veneers</h3>
          <p>Porcelain veneers are more durable and stain-resistant. Composite veneers (bonding) are less invasive and completed in one visit but may need replacement sooner. We'll help you decide based on your goals and budget.</p>

          <h3>Longevity</h3>
          <p>With proper care, porcelain veneers can last 10–15 years or more. We'll guide you on care practices that protect your investment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>Are veneers permanent?</summary><p>Veneers require minimal enamel removal, which is irreversible. That said, they can be replaced when needed, so your smile isn't locked in forever.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Will veneers look natural?</summary><p>Yes—we custom-match shade, shape, and translucency to your surrounding teeth so veneers enhance your smile without looking fake or overdone.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Does getting veneers hurt?</summary><p>The process involves minimal preparation under local anesthesia. Most patients experience little to no discomfort during or after the procedure.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Can veneers be whitened later?</summary><p>Porcelain veneers don't respond to whitening treatments. If you plan to whiten your teeth, it's best to do so before getting veneers so we can match the shade.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Schedule a veneer consultation</h3><p>Consultations typically 30–45 min</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Custom fabrication takes about 1–2 weeks</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Most insurance accepted &amp; verified</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>Precision-matched to your natural teeth</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule a Veneer Consultation</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
